HEADWORD: Unpaired
<hw>Un*paired</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not paired; not
suited or matched.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>And minds <qex>unpaired</qex> had better think alone.</q>
<rj><qau>Crabbe.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unpalped</ent>⟦br⟧
